title: DoctorAdventures - Riley Reid (Throat Treatment) NEW 19 March 20
description: Riley Reid comes into the doctor’s office complaining that her throat is sore and she’s losing her voice. Dr. Johnny Castle examines her thoroughly, and determines that it’s a case of chronic throat tightness- a common ailment that can be rectified completely with an extensive regimen of throat massage, as well as some general stress relief as a preventative measure. It seems that the procedure is working, with Riley becoming more vocal the more extensive the treatment becomes!
